DESIGN SYSTEM INSTRUCTIONS FOR GENERATION:
- Layout: Desktop 1440px grid, center-aligned layout, 12-column setup for sections.
- Color Palette (Mental model for UI): Deep Royal Blue for primary structure (trust), slate for secondary texts, light grayish-blue for background cards and warning text containers.
- Typography: Clean, legible sans-serif font scale (e.g., Inter or Roboto style hierarchy).
- Components: Use distinct styles for primary buttons, radio items, text field containers, and downloadable cards.